name: Nebuchadnezzer
description:
The StarLord has set his eyes on your home planet, Sauna. The Intercom is being monitored by the StarFleet. The only hope is for you to escape them and reach Sauna to alert them of the impending danger.

Luckily you have a warp drive that can teleport you through a black hole. Reach the blackhole which teleports you nearer to Sauna.
